Tasker needs some basic information in order to perform the wellness tracking for you. Additional dialogs will collect the necessary configuration data, some of which is used to unlock your phone.
All data collected is stored on your device.
### NOTE ### Your phone must be locked using a PIN or Tasker won't be able to unlock it. Tracking is still possible, if your phone is unlocked at the time Tasker attempts it.
If you need to change your phone's lock type, you can do this after completing this setup routine. This setup routine can also be run at any time by enabling the setup profile, then opening VirginPulse.
